{"tid":1787171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家諗下你地人生中受過最大的傷害，最大的痛苦係乜野","createTime":"2019-12-17T17:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T17:21:59.000Z","uid":280324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a698dd27d8ca7e570bf28beacea1013fd10e7b","tid":1787171,"uid":280324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"記得有個開槍黑警話佢開槍後受到的精神痛苦比在街上比人擲汽油彈更煎熬，聽完後我覺得人生最痛苦的時候從來都不是比人攻擊你肉體，在街頭上武鬥我們的確是佔下風，但要令黑警受傷害其實有很多層面可以入手，希望大家冷靜地集思廣益，諗下你人生中最大的痛苦同傷害係咩，諗下有無可能比黑警感受到同樣的傷害，令黑警痛苦極大化，大家一齊努力從呢個方向諗就會發現除左街上肢體衝突之外，我們其實仲有好多戰線可以打，可以持續令呢班黑警生不如死"},{"pid":"7b148a9b68126f336b118bbf4cf5e62b5504576d","tid":1787171,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">日程表</span></span></strong><br />\n－－－－－－<strong><em>活動集合</em></strong>－－－－－－</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 12 &middot; 21 </span><br />\n杜絕政治酬庸集會</strong></span><br />\n- 13:00 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1782177/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1782177/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">元朗恐襲五個月</span></strong><br />\n- 15:00 元朗站、港鐵商場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1785918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1785918</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 12 &middot; 22 </span><br />\n聲援維吾爾族人權集會</strong></span><br />\n- 15:30 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1782177/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1782177/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">星期二 12 &middot; 24 </span><br />\n願平安歸香港行動</strong></span><br />\n- 19:00 各區商場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg